<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #2d3436;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7 0%, #a8a4e6 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    .benefits {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .benefits ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .benefits li {
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding-left: 25px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .benefits li:before {
      content: "✓";
      color: #6c5ce7;
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #6c5ce7;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 25px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #636e72;
    }
    .social-links {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .social-links a {
      color: #6c5ce7;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Our Fashion Community!</h1>
      <p>Thank you for joining our style-savvy family</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear Fashion Enthusiast,</p>

      <p>We're thrilled to welcome you to our exclusive fashion community! Thank you for subscribing to our newsletter. Get ready to embark on a journey through the latest trends, sustainable fashion insights, and exclusive style tips.</p>

      <div class="benefits">
        <h3>What's in Store for You:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Early access to new collections and exclusive drops</li>
          <li>Special subscriber-only discounts</li>
          <li>Sustainable fashion guides and tips</li>
          <li>Behind-the-scenes content and designer interviews</li>
          <li>Style inspiration and lookbooks</li>
          <li>Exclusive event invitations</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>As a welcome gift, enjoy <strong>15% off</strong> your first purchase with code: <strong>WELCOME15</strong></p>

      <%= link_to "Start Shopping Now", root_url, class: "cta-button" %>

      <p>Stay tuned for our next email featuring our latest collection and style tips curated just for you!</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>Your Fashion Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="social-links">
        Follow us on:
        <%= link_to "Instagram", "https://instagram.com/yourfashionstore" %> |
        <%= link_to "Facebook", "https://facebook.com/yourfashionstore" %> |
        <%= link_to "Pinterest", "https://pinterest.com/yourfashionstore" %>
      </div>

      <p>
        You received this email because you signed up for our newsletter.
        <%= link_to "Unsubscribe", @unsubscribe_url %> if you prefer not to receive these emails.
      </p>
      
      <p>© <%= Time.current.year %> Your Fashion Store. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 